    <div id="offer">
      <h1>WHAT WE OFFER</h1>
      <p>
        Our goal is to create a safe and inclusive space where individuals can
        connect with others who are experiencing similar mental health
        challenges. We want to offer resources and support to those who may feel
        isolated or alone in their struggles. The platform will include features
        such as support groups, peer-to-peer messaging, and mental health
        resources. We also plan to partner with mental health professionals to
        provide expert advice and support. As we continue to develop and refine
        our platform, we are constantly keeping the needs and experiences of our
        users in mind. We believe that by creating a space that prioritizes
        mental health, we can help individuals on their journey towards healing
        and recovery.
      </p>
